1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:12,000
A jailbroken agent runs code as root inside the sandbox.
IronClaw assumes it already won.

2
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:28,000
Escape 1, phone home to exfiltrate.
network=none, only loopback exists. Denied.

3
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:44,000
Escape 2, read the operator host.
The host root is outside the sandbox namespace. Denied.

4
00:00:44,000 --> 00:01:00,000
Escape 3, seize the Docker Engine socket.
It was never mounted in. Denied.

5
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:12,000
3 of 3 escapes denied. The box held.
Isolation you can prove, not just promise.

